* 『'''{{ill|Monthly Public Safety Forum|ja|月刊治安フォーラム|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Monthly Public Safety Forum|qq=}}'''』, September 2007 Issue
* {{ill|Koichi Toyama|ja|外山恒一|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koichi Toyama|qq=}} and {{ill|Fumito Nakagawa|ja|中川文人|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fumito Nakagawa|qq=}}, eds., 『Post-Student Movement History: The Hōdaikuro Hel Edition 1985–1994』, Sairyusha, January 2010, ISBN 477911487X
* Comprehensive Magazine for Transformation “Jōkyō” (Spring 2020 Issue) {{ill|Jōkyō Publishing|ja|情況出版|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōkyō Publishing|qq=}}

